=Description=

"CoinTelegraph got a chance to catch up with Vitalik Buterin at CEBE 2014 in Vienna and Dr. Gavin Wood at Bitcoin2014 in Amsterdam. Buterin and Wood are both from Ethereum, which recently raised over 3,700 BTC in the first 12 hours of its Ether crowdsale.

Ethereum is certainly one of the most exciting and highly-anticipated Crypto 2.0 projects right now, so we had to get the latest news and developments on the Ethereum platform, crypto 2.0, and their thoughts in general on everything from Bitcoin to Web 3.0. 

For the creators and leading lights of such an influential part of cryptocurrency innovation, the two were surprisingly level-headed as they explained more behind their work and the current scene surrounding the conference. Gavin additionally had some handy advice for young entrepreneurs seeking to enter the cryptospace, including pointers for study and development of expertise."
(http://cointelegraph.com/news/112145/cutting-edge-an-interview-with-ethereum-creators-vitalik-buterin-and-gavin-wood)


